                        <td>
                            
                            <b> ANC.DT.19 Hepatitis B diagnosis:</b> 
                            
                            <br/>
                            
                            <b>When:</b>
                            
                            <i>Named Event:</i> ANC.B10.4. Diagnosis and treatment
                            <br/>
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            <b>Then:</b>
                            <table class="grid-dict">
                                
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        
                                        Counselling:
– Provide post-testing counselling
– Advise retesting and immunisation if ongoing risk or known exposure
                                        
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        <b>If:</b>
                                        
                                        <i>Applicability:</i>
                                        
                                        &quot;Hepatitis B test result&quot; = &quot;Hepatitis B negative&quot;
                                        
                                        <i>(Should Provide hepatitis B counselling and immunization)</i>
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        
                                        Counseling:
– Provide post-testing counselling
– Request confirmatory nucleic acid testing (NAT)
– Refer to hospital
                                        
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        <b>If:</b>
                                        
                                        <i>Applicability:</i>
                                        
                                        &quot;Hepatitis B test result&quot; = &quot;Hepatitis B positive&quot;
                                        
